headline: The Stock Market Beyond Nvidia: Walmart, Target Earnings, And Bitcoin's March To $100K
summary: Things could quiet down just a little on the stock market in the coming week, giving investors plenty of space in which to focus on Nvidia's earnings report.  It is likely that news from Washington will be ongoing, as President-elect Donald Trump continues to assemble the players for his administration.  Investors will get a closer look at China's EV war, and bitcoin is well worth watching, to see whether it edges closer to the $100,000 mark.
